Commands to Run Tomorrow (Every Time You Start)

  Open 3 terminals and run:
                                          
  Terminal 1: Start the Server
                                                                                                        cd C:\Users\Srikumaran\Desktop\hubspot-codeflow
  npm run dev                                                                                         
  
  Terminal 2: Start ngrok

  ngrok http 3100

  Terminal 3: (Only if you make code changes)

  cd C:\Users\Srikumaran\Desktop\hubspot-codeflow\codeflow-project
  hs project upload
  hs project deploy --build=<number>

