  ---
  Important Note About ngrok

  âš ï¸ Free ngrok gives a new URL each time!

  Tomorrow when you start ngrok, you'll get a different URL. You'll need to:

  1. Copy the new ngrok URL
  2. Update .env file: BASE_URL=https://new-url.ngrok-free.dev
  3. Update codeflow-project/src/app/workflow-actions/workflow-actions-hsmeta.json: change actionUrl  
  4. Update codeflow-project/src/app/CodeFlow-hsmeta.json: change redirectUrls
  5. Run hs project upload && hs project deploy

  ---
  Now go check HubSpot workflows and search for "CodeFlow"! ğŸ‰
  

  
  1. Send Webhook Action:
    - URL: https://httpbin.org/post
    - Method: POST
    - Body: {"test": "data"}
  2. Run Code Action:
    - Inline Code: output.output1 = 'Success!';